== Headline ==

A validator for [[Language:XSD]]

== Description ==

XSDValidator is a [[@technology]]; it is a XSD-specific validator. XSDValidator relies on System.Xml.Schema API to parse the file and report the errors discovered. Zero exit code is to be interpreted as successful validation; non-zero exit code as failure.

== Usage ==

To build and execute the validator, you need to have Mono SDK (2.10 +) installed.
Use 'make build' to build the project.

